These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade
There 2 different types of food: artichoke, grapes
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, family
1. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the person eating grapes##8
2. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
3. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | cola      |
| Food          | grapes | artichoke    |
| Hobby         | skydiving   | filmmaking |
| Movie-Genre   | satire  | family      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, tea
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, hiking
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, accountant
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, ship
1. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the fisherman##5
3. the accountant is not to the right of the fisherman##8
4. the person driving the subway is not the person who's hobby is hiking##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | milk        | tea    |
| Hobby       | card-games         | hiking |
| Job         | accountant | fisherman   |
| Transport   | subway               | ship  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, action
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, country
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, british
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, turtle
1. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
2. the british is not to the right of the owner of the turtle##8
3. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the left of the person watching action movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical       | action |
| Music-Genre   | r&b       | country    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | british |
| Pet           | guinea-pig        | turtle   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
