2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##8
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Hobby         | cooking | filmmaking  |
| Job           | videographer  | writer |
| Nationality   | malaysian | british   |
| Transport     | snowmobile   | scooter |

