2. the person driving the train is the person driving the train##1
3. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the paramedic##5
4. the person driving the train is not to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##8
5. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the left of the person eating spinach##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
