There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, russian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, skateboarding
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the canadian is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person driving the airplane is not the person watching martial-arts movies##6
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts      | zombie |
| Nationality   | canadian    | russian   |
| Sport         | skateboarding | cycling     |
| Transport     | jet-ski | airplane  |

